{"tid":465610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［新會然學開po]其實香港人冇咁自私嘅話，所有事都會運作得快啲","createTime":"2017-11-11T16:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T10:57:20.000Z","uid":157799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c273efe7402fe32df5e4eae82dcab1efffba303b","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"每日搭地鐵都成鳩日臨閂門嗰刻有一班仆街衝入嚟，搞到道門都唔知要重開幾多次，delay咗勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明下班車係兩分鐘之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住啲黃衫舉牌開哂咪叫班仆街行入車廂中間，個個郁都唔撚郁，出面一大班上唔到車嘅人目放架空車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同班自私撚終於逼完個地鐵，月台搭電梯上地面嗰陣真係講撚曬粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班仆街想快啲就好心排隊啦，成炸人爭嚟爭去真係唔會快啲，次次都係車立口位啲人流停咗喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋逼巴士你地班仆街都唔好撚逼人走，其實繁忙時刻，巴士司機好多時都會等多陣先閂閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前我企巴士下層要逼到去落車位個門口，當我準備落車俾其他人落咗先再上翻，有個死廢中係都要落車先，跟住佢就係咁想逼開我，我一路淡淡定望住佢喺到on99咁逼，一路想搵位落車俾佢了咗個心願佢（呢啲廢中真係到時去死都要咁進取至好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），但係我完全俾佢夾住咗落唔撚到去，佢喺門口到前後推咗大概5次左右，後面塞住咗成班要落車嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢終於逼到落去，我就終於可以落到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成條隊好似屙完第一嚿屎之後咁暢順咁落哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以其實只要俾2秒俾前面嘅人行咗先，唔好只顧自己，成件事會快好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開呢個po希望大家睇到可以唔好再爭先恐後，一嚟真係好劣質，二嚟件事真係唔會快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我平時見就係啲20幾30歲啲西裝友OL同大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以唔好話冇連登氣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c108be2d4fb345c601dc4dcab67f9239f5cc311","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c4110406929d2af89a04f4f187d2f377b05d0007","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0481356affda0985336352310c3f51d5c0ca54fb","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c558e04019603fa32d6cec8e1cae02ec3efadcac","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:53:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ff164dc15b7a513ac66e0886a777237b54fb3430","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3a8c378913d658b7f5b137656ce8e1f5f7567f21","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:58:49.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5feed7f2f03765eccaa2897a7d1dac382c0fdcc9","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cb790c1a8281ab773c92df9965e21575c2b24aa9","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"一朝起身連埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce45b8de5f42d5a7332d482b061391b81bf13cb","tid":465610,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"512a1765b1b04f7c5c93e1998f30af3098755f6a","tid":465610,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}